    "45401": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Razor",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Who's there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Chill out Razor, it's only us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "You... are also knight?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...So you don't know each other after all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"The red one, burny girl...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That wasn't Amber?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "No. This girl also red, but not so burny like other girl."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "This is starting to make sense. Is this the wolf boy you were talking about?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Correct! His name is Razor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Help me out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "With what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "No time. I sent Lupical away. People coming, bad people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Those guys from earlier?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I understand. But first, I have a few questions—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "*sniff* I smell blood. Quick."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Blood? I hope the wolves didn't attack those idiots..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "45410": {
        "Desc": "Check for strange things along the way",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "45411": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Amber",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Blood droplets!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Not human blood, wolf blood. Lupical blood..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Loopy what now? Are you gonna tell us what it means yet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Lupical is family fate gave me. When wolf accepts human as its own. Or human accepts wolf. That is Lupical."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds like gibberish to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "That's strange, where does the word come from? Surely it wasn't made up by the wolves?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "It's just the name he gave."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "...Who's \"he\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Guardian of this land."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wouldn't that be Barbatos though? He is the ruler of Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Enough. Another clue. Follow me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Hey, wait! This is your chance to prove your innocence!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He's already gone!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "45412": {
        "Desc": "Catch up to Razor",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "45413": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Razor",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "This is him. We find his blood. Bad men did this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How terrible..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "I do agree that it's awful. But that doesn't change the fact that—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "We didn't attack village! Not us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "A black wolf and his pack, not from here. They try to take over land. They broke the code."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "<color=#00E1FFFF>Whose code?</color>"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Guardian of this land."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "That's now the second time you've brought that up. Tell us who that is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "I take Lupical further in. Follow me, maybe you see."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
