    "45415": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Razor about how to help the injured wolf",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Where are we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, help me. Collect these."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aren't those wolfhook seeds?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Crush them. Put on wound. Bleeding stop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "It's true. Wolfhook seeds have a liquid coating that not only functions as a mild painkiller, but also has a hemostatic effect..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "...I read that in a book."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "...I have no idea."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Hooks help seeds move. Liquid stops pain and bleeding."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Animal doesn't feel hooks, they take seeds far away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "...Purple teacher told me so."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "I stay here, take care of this one. I answer red girl's questions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Right. And if that lot does come back, I doubt they will try their luck against a member of the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "#Your wolf friend is not clear of my suspicion just yet. But {NICKNAME}, we'll still need to fetch those seeds."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "45402": {
        "Desc": "Collect Wolfhook",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Traveler, go and find some Wolfhooks. I need to talk with Razor."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "45403": {
        "Desc": "Give a Wolfhook to Razor",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're back! Have we got enough?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Yes. Enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Razor was just telling me about the wolven code of conduct. Mind-blowing stuff."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "We've looked everywhere and haven't seen any other wolves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jotun",
                    "T": "Yep, that's wolves for you. The one we managed to capture must have been sick or something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "Wh—What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "Revenge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jotun",
                    "T": "It's him! The one who was raised by wolves!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "So, it was you. I should have known, wolves aren't smart enough to be behind this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "I can't believe you would help wolves plot against humans!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hopkins the Marvelous",
                    "T": "They throw you some scraps and you treat them like kin? Have you forgotten what you are?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Amber",
                    "T": "Enough!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! You can't talk about Razor like that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jotun",
                    "T": "The Knights of Favonius are gonna let this guy off!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Razor",
                    "T": "We. Did. Not. Raid. Village."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
